<doc id="1160268" wikidata="Q5014355" url="?curid=1160268" title="Arkansas-class ironclad">
<text>The &quot;Arkansas&quot;-class ironclads were a class of two casemate ironclads ordered by the Confederate States Navy in 1861 to operate in the Western and Trans-Mississippi theaters of the American Civil War.

