===Later films===
Subsequently, revisionist themes have prevailed in Western film production. Major releases from 1971 to the present include:
* &quot;Lawman&quot; (1971)
* &quot;McCabe &amp; Mrs. Miller&quot; (1971)
* &quot;Jeremiah Johnson&quot; (1972)
* &quot;Chato&#x27;s Land&quot; (1972) 
