* &quot;The Outlaw Josey Wales&quot; (1976) 
* &quot;The Long Riders&quot; (1980)
* &quot;Pale Rider&quot; (1985)
* &quot;Dances With Wolves&quot; (1990)
* &quot;Unforgiven&quot; (1992)
* &quot;The Ballad of Little Jo&quot; (1993)
* &quot;&quot; (1993)
